<L>__{exterior manhattan day}
<A>__{a suitcase in each hand, johana gets out of the cab and walks up the stairs of her apartment.}
<L>__{interior hallway day}
<A>__{johana puts down her suitcase wearily. catches her breath and gets out her keys. she tries one in the top lock. it doesn't work. she tries harder. there's a woman's voice yelling angrily from inside the apartment.}
